<sentence type="quasi">再度挑戦</sentence>
<sentence>　近藤さんは門真市に<event class="" eid="e73">お住まいで</event><TIMEX3 definite="FALSE" tid="t13" type="DURATION" value="P69Y" valueFromSurface="P69Y">六十九歳</TIMEX3>。</sentence>
<sentence>碁を<event class="" eid="e74">覚えた</event>のは<TIMEX3 definite="FALSE" tid="t14" type="DURATION" value="P17Y" valueFromSurface="P17Y">十七歳</TIMEX3>の頃で<quote>「田舎の郵便局長に<event class="" eid="e75">教わった</event>」</quote>と<event class="" eid="e76">いう</event>。</sentence>
<sentence>　もっぱら碁会所で腕を<event class="" eid="e77">磨かれ</event>、アマ本因坊大阪代表や最強戦<sampling type="end" />関西代表などの棋歴が<event class="" eid="e78">ある</event>。</sentence>
